msgctxt "692"
msgid "Isawa"
msgstr "Isawa"

msgctxt "696"
msgid "Talk_Angry"
msgstr "Talk_Angry"

msgctxt "68_Isawa"
msgid "All right. You listen, and you listen good. Fay's <Italic>my</Italic> girl.\\r\n"\n"Only I know how to treat her like the lady she is. But you?\\r\n"\n"Compared to me, you're jack shit－and about to be dead meat!"
msgstr "De acuerdo. Escúchame bien. Fay es <Italic>mi</Italic> chica. Solo yo se\\r\n"\n"tratarla como se merece. ¿Y tú? Comparado a mi eres\\r \n"\n"una mierda－¡una mierda con las horas contadas!"

